{
  "stem": "10564.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943, '44, we work for the Steinbruch I work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means I blow the mountain so that people have can get gravels so the Goeth can build himself a road to this garage where HE have the cars, the mechanic working for him.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I remember we set the fuses, we connect the fuses together, and the master give us a cigarette to light the fuse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because easier with a cigarette to light the fuse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got a red flag.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anybody coming on the front gate from outside to inside camp, we should stop them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this road is right next to the mountain when we drill the holes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anybody can drive there can be killed because the stones flying everywhere, big chunks of rocks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember I was far away, maybe about a half a mile or maybe a little less. 1,000, 1,200, 1,500 feet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- and then we set fire, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means that we ignited the fuses, and everything is-- you think that we should be watching.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the people hide behind the mountain, or behind this, or behind barracks, behind this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when I was maybe about 50 feet from the gate, and I saw from far away that a car, a Mercedes Benz with a big old hard top down, with four people in it and a driver coming straight to the gate.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, by the time, the fuse only take a few seconds there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They open the fuse, they opened the gate, and he's coming through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The red flag.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dynamite, everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the driver couldn't hear me, so he tried to take a gun, and the driver driving took a gun for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
